      <odd id="aspace_72a0486a5eb6eee139c84c5af76a3b47">
         <head>General</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 13-I-2 (YRG 13-I-2), Records of the master of Morse College.</p>  
      </odd>
  
      <prefercite id="aspace_7aa38bcd2639c22cffbc630e635ec594">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Pierson College, Yale University, Records of the Master (RU 316). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_a144e26c9e65c8978aee0216dacf6b3c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of the administrative files and memorabilia of Stanton Wheeler, Master of Morse College from 1995-2001.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <bioghist id="aspace_b6f120aa4784951ec4e177928e812f62">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The title "Master" for chief executive officers of residential colleges was changed to "Head of College" in April of 2016.</p>  
      </bioghist>
